snippet.title: Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Take-Down - Missions in Korea - Operation: Sudden Assault
snippet.description: Sixth mission of Tom Clancy's Rainbow Six: Take-Down - Missions in Korea - Operation: Sudden Assault. Played on elite mode while going solo. This mission takes place in a town where you need to kill off terrorist leaders, terrorists, and rescue some hostages.
